9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to firearms; amending 21 O.S. 2021,
Sections 1279 and 1280, which relate to pointing
11 firearms at others and related penalties; clarifying
scope of and exception to certain unlawful act;
12 deleting mandatory minimum sentencing option;
deleting handgun license revocation requirement;
13 amending 21 O.S. 2021, Sections 1289.16 and 1289.25,
which relate to the Oklahoma Firearms Act of 1971;
14 authorizing the pointing of firearms under certain
circumstances; making certain acts unlawful; deleting
15 administrative penalty provision; expanding
situations that allow for the use of physical or
16 deadly force; allowing for the defensive display of
firearms under certain circumstances; providing
17 exceptions; defining terms; and declaring an
emergency.
